    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《永恒沉眠：爱与杀戮的乐园》是一款悬疑、推理、爱情题材的AVG游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作玩法为特殊的精神陪审团机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标并非揭发真实的真相，而是站在己方立场上逆推和证明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战胜对立方，以此获得更多精神信徒，赢得审判最终的胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras/2e39b9f9afcd0d0afe51194ee07064c1.avif?t=1756792525\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras_big/2e39b9f9afcd0d0afe51194ee07064c1.avif?t=1756792525 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>梦境搜查</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于日月分野的梦境国度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精神与现实的缝隙中获取证据。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精神审判</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精神陪审团机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比起真相，更重要的是民心所向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用人证与物证，赢得审判的胜利。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现实博弈</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作、对立亦或是背叛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位主角将走向截然不同的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为信仰而生的纷争，由你来决定世界的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras/63b67d722487135814612fd59e891f5b.avif?t=1756792525\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras_big/63b67d722487135814612fd59e891f5b.avif?t=1756792525 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>男女双主角</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >男刑警与女侦探， 截然不同的性格与选择。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双线叙事</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换立场和视角，感受宿命般的局势变幻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras/b95429ce509193d630591e5895896c8e.avif?t=1756792525\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426060/extras_big/b95429ce509193d630591e5895896c8e.avif?t=1756792525 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古未来风</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古与前卫并存的世界。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样的可攻略角色</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与角色们建立超越传统的爱憎羁绊。</p>",
